{"tid":1468221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機場事後嘅小小心得","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:22.000Z","uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"538a7d7f703c5bc17ffa6ef3b895a486bc199170","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:07:50.000Z","msg":"其實當佢揾人扮示威者/記者個陣 佢已經諗好盤棋點捉 <br />\n<br />\n佢揾狗扮示威者 目的就係想我地疑神疑鬼 想我地不停互捉 想我地分化/瘋狂覺得人係鬼 但我地偏偏俾佢達成左佢嘅目的 宜家見人戴單邊耳機/大大隻就覺得人係鬼(小弟係其中一個) 搞到成個集會都彌漫住負面情緒 宜家揾人扮埋記者 咁我地係咪要捉埋記者鬼？<br />\n希望大家記住 我地係機場嘅集會係和平 係冇衝突 即使d狗車泊到成個機場都係 佢都無位可以入到我地 反而你去圍警車 打狗 圍鬼 只會令到成場運動好核突<br />\n<br />\n希望大家記住 即使在場有鬼 請大家諗下 佢有咩可入到我地？有咩情報可以俾到上頭？銅鑼灣個陣佢地混入都話可以俾下上頭知前線位置 等上頭佈處 但機場有咩可以報？現場環境十分和平 有人高叫口號呀？佢地根本無用武之處 咁聰明嘅我諗你都明班狗想點啦 倒不如唔好理佢 由佢影由佢望 我有我叫 佢有佢on99企係到<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想你地唔捉 係想你捉到但用第2種方法令佢難堪敗走 見到佢係鬼嘅 咪影低話俾手足聽 叫佢地行過見到叫聲「支持香港警察嚴正執法 講笑炸 傻豬」咁 撚下佢 好過圍住佢 令到其他旅客覺得我地人多蝦人少 <br />\n<br />\n希望大家記得當初 我地由69到宜家 行到呢到係好辛苦嘅事 我地係邁向緊成功咖 唔好因爲咁而放棄我地當初「不指責，不割蓆，不分化」嘅宗旨 香港人一定要團結呀！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己香港自己救</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警死全家</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPs. 小弟講野唔叻 希望大家一齊討論下！"},{"pid":"fb235720ea756cc22a3e5a7c24070e00f0e92578","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"自推10野"},{"pid":"5a3640d67865a5d892361550b30b930a06760865","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:28.000Z","msg":"10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e295b47e18379e825f4e6c04e639a2bc6a92ee1","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:08:41.000Z","msg":"9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb01e8afa5efc3791b24eed6a8afe5de9ef1ebd","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:01.000Z","msg":"8<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa26a93b72b6c06fb3d30257911a8ee0f79c59d","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9b4d51a36fcbaf4f5f14f85a684cb6674c6c11","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:30.000Z","msg":"6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa925bb4e294a3b111475684b680b352f0b27360","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:43.000Z","msg":"5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ce2221556c593796742a07e0aee2be91b4c39e","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:09:56.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a830afbdc92270d947c1949857cb4e3ecd673f","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:14.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0a595eb1146a7ce601555fc00dd67657d6b7c5","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:26.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9a4ee39199febb210ecae708a87107cc4bbeb7","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:10:43.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbc05a9dc8b4572671432899508652a470256d1e","tid":1468221,"uid":151017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT